  ('franks-redhot-creamy-garlic-chicken-mcmuffin-english-muffin-5', 'franks-redhot-creamy-garlic-chicken-mcmuffin', 'English Muffin', 'Enriched wheat flour, Water, Yeast, Corn meal and corn flour, Vegetable oil (canola and/or soy oil), Salt, Sugars (sugar, barley malt), May contain any or all of the following in varying proportions: Monoglycerides, Diacetylated tartaric acid esters of mono- and diglycerides, Monocalcium phosphate, Ascorbic acid, Enzymes, Cultured wheat flour, Citric acid, Calcium citrate, Corn starch, Wheat gluten, Fumaric acid, Malted barley flour.', 5),
