*Before cooking.', 52),
  ('quarter-pounder-without-cheese', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Quarter Pounder without Cheese', 'Beef', 'A quarter pound* of 100% Canadian beef topped with tangy pickles, ketchup, mustard and the sweet bite of slivered onions, on a toasted sesame seed bun. It''s a simple recipe, but it works. *Weight before cooking at least 112.3g.', 53),
  ('double-quarter-pounder-with-cheese', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Double Quarter Pounder with Cheese', 'Beef', 'Two quarter pound* 100% Canadian beef patties. Layered with two slices of melty cheese, slivered onions and pickles on sesame seed bun. *Weight  before cooking at least 112.3g .', 54),
  ('double-quarter-pounder-without-cheese', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Double Quarter Pounder without Cheese', 'Beef', 'Two quarter pound* 100% Canadian beef patties layered with tangy pickles, ketchup, mustard and the sweet bite of slivered onions, on a toasted sesame seed bun. *Weight  before cooking at least 112.3g .', 55),
  ('quarter-pounder-blt', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Quarter Pounder BLT', 'Beef', 'Sink your teeth into crisp bacon, juicy tomato and fresh lettuce to reach the beefy, cheesy core of the Quarter Pounder. Did we mention the bacon? There''s bacon.', 56),
  ('double-quarter-pounder-blt', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Double Quarter Pounder BLT', 'Beef', 'Two quarter pound* 100% Canadian beef patties. Layered with a slice of processed cheese, hickory-smoked bacon strips, fresh lettuce, tomato, slivered onions, mayo-style sauce, ketchup, mustard and pickles on a toasted sesame seed bun. 

*Weight before cooking at least 112.3g.', 57),
  ('chicken-big-mac', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Chicken Big Mac', 'Chicken', 'It''s back! The Chicken Big Mac features two patties made with 100% Canadian-raised seasoned chicken breast in a crispy, light-tasting coating, along with the much-loved special sauce, lettuce, processed cheese and pickles. With a side of classic McDonald''s fries, we''d say this sounds like the perfect meal.', 58),
  ('creamy-chipotle-chicken-mcwrap-crispy', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Creamy Chipotle Chicken McWrap - Crispy', 'Chicken', 'Made with 100% Canadian-raised seasoned chicken topped with creamy chipotle sauce, crispy tri-colour tortilla strips, shredded lettuce, sliced tomato and cucumbers. All wrapped in a soft white flour tortilla.', 61),
  ('creamy-chipotle-chicken-mcwrap-grilled', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Creamy Chipotle Chicken McWrap - Grilled', 'Chicken', 'Made with 100% Canadian-raised seasoned chicken topped with creamy chipotle sauce, crispy tri-colour tortilla strips, shredded lettuce, sliced tomato and cucumbers. All wrapped in a soft white flour tortilla.', 62),
  ('sweet-chili-junior-chicken', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Sweet Chili Junior Chicken', 'Chicken', 'Your tastebuds will be singing a whole new tune with a remixed Sweet Chili Junior Chicken made with Canadian-raised crispy seasoned chicken, topped with crunchy shredded lettuce, tangy sweet chili sauce and mayo-style sauce, all on a toasty bun.', 63),
  ('mccrispy', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'McCrispy', 'Chicken', 'The McCrispy is a crispy chicken sandwich made with tender and juicy 100% Canadian-raised seasoned chicken. It''s topped with shredded lettuce and creamy mayo-style sauce and served on a soft potato bun for a taste that''s so McDonald''s.', 64),
  ('spicy-mccrispy', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Spicy McCrispy', 'Chicken', 'The Spicy McCrispy is a crispy chicken sandwich topped with our signature habanero sauce. Made with tender and juicy 100% Canadian-raised seasoned chicken and served on a soft potato bun, it has a taste that''s unmistakably McDonald''s.', 65),
  ('spicy-mccrispy-bacon-deluxe', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Spicy Bacon Deluxe McCrispy Sandwich', 'Chicken', 'The Spicy Bacon Deluxe McCrispy is big on everything, including heat. With our southern-style fried chicken patty on a soft potato bun, topped with shredded lettuce, hickory-smoked bacon, tomato and our spicy Habanero sauce, this sandwich kicks crispy, juicy and tender up to the next level.', 66),
  ('mccrispy-bacon-deluxe', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'McCrispy Bacon Deluxe', 'Chicken', 'Bacon and a slice of fresh tomato take the McCrispy to the next level. Made with crispy, tender and juicy 100% Canadian-raised seasoned chicken, then topped with shredded lettuce, creamy mayo-style sauce and served on a soft potato bun for a taste that''s so McDonald''s.', 67),
  ('mccrispy-with-grilled-chicken', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Grilled Chicken Sandwich', 'Chicken', 'The Grilled Chicken Sandwich is made with tender and juicy 100% Canadian-raised grilled seasoned chicken. Topped with shredded lettuce, creamy mayo-style sauce and served on a soft potato bun for that McD''s flavour you crave.', 68),
  ('bacon-deluxe-mccrispy-sandwich-with-grilled-chicken', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Bacon Deluxe Grilled Chicken Sandwich', 'Chicken', 'Bacon and a slice of fresh tomato take the Grilled Chicken Sandwich to the next level. Made with tender and juicy 100% Canadian-raised grilled seasoned chicken, then topped with shredded lettuce, creamy mayo-style sauce and served on a soft potato bun. This is big flavour in every bite.', 69),
  ('spicy-grilled-chicken-sandwich', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Spicy Grilled Chicken Sandwich', 'Chicken', 'Made with tender and juicy 100% Canadian-raised grilled seasoned chicken, and topped with shredded lettuce and our signature Habanero sauce, it''s a spicy-lovers dream served on a soft potato bun.', 70),
  ('spicy-bacon-deluxe-grilled-chicken-sandwich', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Spicy Bacon Deluxe Grilled Chicken Sandwich', 'Chicken', 'The Spicy Bacon Deluxe Grilled Chicken Sandwich is big on everything, including heat. Made with 100% Canadian-raised grilled seasoned chicken on a soft potato bun, topped with shredded lettuce, hickory-smoked bacon, tomato and our spicy Habanero sauce, this sandwich kicks juicy and tender up to the next level.', 71),
  ('habanero-mcchicken-sandwich', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Spicy Habanero McChicken', 'Chicken', 'Our classic McChicken packed with a punch! This spicy Habanero McChicken is topped with our creamy Habanero sauce. Perfectly breaded seasoned chicken, crisp shredded lettuce, all on a freshly toasted sesame bun. Some ingredients are just meant to be together.', 72),
  ('mcchicken', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'McChicken', 'Chicken', 'Breaded seasoned chicken and crisp lettuce, topped with our Mayo-Style Sauce. Some ingredients are just meant to be together.', 73),
  ('junior-chicken', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Junior Chicken', 'Chicken', 'You don''t need to compromise with the great taste of a Junior Chicken sandwich, made with chicken raised on Canadian farms, at a price you can always feel good about.', 74),
  ('4-chicken-mcnuggets', 'mcdonalds-canada', '4 Chicken McNuggets', 'Chicken', 'No artificial flavours, colours or preservatives. Made with 100% seasoned chicken breast, the Chicken McNuggets you crave are still simply delicious.', 75),
  ('6-chicken-mcnuggets', 'mcdonalds-canada', '6 Chicken McNuggets', 'Chicken', 'No artificial flavours, colours or preservatives. Made with 100% seasoned chicken breast, the Chicken McNuggets you crave are still simply delicious.', 76),
  ('10-chicken-mcnuggets', 'mcdonalds-canada', '10 Chicken McNuggets', 'Chicken', 'No artificial flavours, colours or preservatives. Made with 100% seasoned chicken breast, the Chicken McNuggets you crave are still simply delicious.', 77),
  ('20-chicken-mcnuggets', 'mcdonalds-canada', '20 Chicken McNuggets (Serves 2)', 'Chicken', 'No artificial flavours, colours or preservatives. Made with 100% seasoned chicken breast, the Chicken McNuggets you crave are still simply delicious.', 78),
  ('spicy-buffalo-chicken-poutine', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Spicy Buffalo Chicken Poutine (Quebec)', 'Chicken', 'Made with our World Famous Fries layered with stringy cheese curds and savoury gravy and topped with crispy pieces of 100% Canadian raised seasoned chicken, drizzled with spicy buffalo sauced and topped with chopped green onions. Only offered in Quebec.', 79),
  ('happy-meal-snack-wrap-crispy', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Chicken Snack Wrap Happy Meal with Crispy Chicken', 'Chicken', 'Made with 100% Canadian-raised seasoned chicken topped with shredded lettuce and mayo-style sauce wrapped in a soft white flour tortilla. Try one today with your choice of apple slices or mini/small fries, yogurt and small/child-size drink (as applicable).', 80),
  ('spicy-buffalo-snack-wrap-grilled', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Spicy Buffalo Chicken Snack Wrap with Grilled Chicken', 'Chicken', 'Made with 100% Canadian raised seasoned chicken topped with shredded lettuce, shredded cheese and spicy buffalo sauce wrapped in a soft white flour tortilla.', 81),
  ('spicy-buffalo-snack-wrap-crispy', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Spicy Buffalo Chicken Snack Wrap with Crispy Chicken', 'Chicken', 'Made with 100% Canadian raised seasoned chicken topped with shredded lettuce, shredded cheese and spicy buffalo sauce wrapped in a soft white flour tortilla.', 82),
  ('new-sweet-chili-mcwrap-grilled', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Sweet Chili McWrap', 'Chicken', 'Made with 100% Canadian raised seasoned chicken topped with shredded lettuce, cucumbers, mayo-style sauce and sweet chili sauce. All wrapped up in a soft white flour tortilla.', 83),
  ('new-sweet-chili-mcwrap-crispy', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Sweet Chili McWrap', 'Chicken', 'Made with 100% Canadian raised seasoned chicken topped with shredded lettuce, sliced tomato, cucumbers, mayo-style sauce and sweet chili sauce. All wrapped up in a soft white flour tortilla.', 84),
  ('new-chicken-and-bacon-mcwrap-crispy', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Chicken & Bacon McWrap', 'Chicken', 'Made with 100% Canadian raised seasoned chicken topped with shredded lettuce, sliced tomato, cucumbers, hickory-smoked bacon and mayo-style sauce. All wrapped up in a soft white flour tortilla.', 85),
  ('new-chicken-and-bacon-mcwrap-grilled', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Chicken & Bacon McWrap', 'Chicken', 'Made with 100% Canadian raised seasoned chicken topped with shredded lettuce, sliced tomato, cucumbers, hickory-smoked bacon and mayo-style sauce. All wrapped up in a soft white flour tortilla.', 86),
  ('ranch-chicken-snack-wrap-grilled-for-relaunch', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Ranch Chicken Snack Wrap with Grilled Chicken', 'Chicken', 'Made with 100% Canadian raised seasoned chicken topped with shredded lettuce, shredded cheese and ranch sauce wrapped in a soft white flour tortilla.', 87),
  ('ranch-chicken-snack-wrap-crispy-for-relaunch', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Ranch Chicken Snack Wrap with Crispy Chicken', 'Chicken', 'Made with 100% Canadian raised seasoned chicken topped with shredded lettuce, shredded cheese and ranch sauce wrapped in a soft white flour tortilla.', 88),
  ('mcveggie', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'McVeggie', 'Sandwiches & Wraps', 'A breaded veggie patty made with a blend of vegetables (including carrots, green beans, zucchini, peas, soybeans, broccoli and corn) and seasoning, topped with shredded lettuce and creamy mayo-style sauce, served on a toasted sesame bun.', 89),
  ('spicy-mcveggie', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Spicy McVeggie', 'Sandwiches & Wraps', 'A breaded veggie patty made with a blend of vegetables (including carrots, green beans, zucchini, peas, soybeans, broccoli and corn) and seasoning, topped with shredded lettuce and creamy Habanero sauce, served on a toasted sesame bun.', 90),
  ('filet-o-fish', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Filet-O-Fish', 'Sandwiches & Wraps', 'Dive right in. Our Filet-O-Fish is pure temptation on a lightly steamed bun, topped with processed cheese and tangy tartar sauce.', 91),
  ('double-filet-o-fish', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Double Filet-O-Fish', 'Sandwiches & Wraps', 'Bite into not one, but two crisp and flaky white fish filets. Topped with processed cheese and tangy tartar sauce, it''s double the delicious on a warm steamed bun.', 92),
  ('happy-meal-snack-wrap-grilled', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Chicken Snack Wrap Happy Meal with Grilled Chicken', 'Sandwiches & Wraps', 'Made with 100% Canadian-raised seasoned chicken topped with shredded lettuce and mayo-style sauce wrapped in a soft white flour tortilla. Try one today with your choice of apple slices or mini/small fries, yogurt and small/child-size drink (as applicable).', 93),
  ('Baked-Blueberry-Cream-Cheese-Pie', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Baked Blueberry Cream Cheese  Pie', 'Snacks & Sides', 'Made with blueberries and a sweet cream cheese filling wrapped in a flaky crust, baked fresh daily and served warm.', 94),
  ('chewy-chocolate-chunk-cookie', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Chewy Chocolate Chunk Cookie', 'Snacks & Sides', 'A classic chewy, soft-baked cookie made with decadent chocolate chunks.', 95),
  ('rainbow-sprinkle-cookie', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Rainbow Sprinkle Cookie', 'Snacks & Sides', 'A soft-baked cookie bursting with sprinkles and sweet white confectionary pieces.', 96),
  ('toasted-smores-cookie', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Toasted S''mores Cookie', 'Snacks & Sides', 'Enjoy the cozy flavour of this soft-baked cookie loaded with marshmallows, chocolate chips and graham-style pieces.', 97),
  ('chocolate-chip-muffin', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Chocolate Chip Muffin', 'Snacks & Sides', 'Baked fresh daily, the Chocolate Chip Muffin is sweet and delicious, mixed with milk chocolate chips and topped with more milk chocolate chips.', 98),
  ('apple-slices', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Apple Slices', 'Snacks & Sides', 'A crisp and delicious snack, prepared for fruit lovers on the go.', 99),
  ('french-fries-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'World Famous Fries', 'Snacks & Sides', 'McDonald''s World Famous Fries are always a delicious choice. Cut from whole potatoes grown on Canadian farms, our fries are cooked to golden perfection in a vegetable oil blend. Mmmm... of course you want fries with that!', 100),
  ('mini-fry', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Mini Fry', 'Snacks & Sides', 'World famous fries in a mini size! Cut from whole potatoes grown on Canadian farms, our fries are cooked to golden perfection in a vegetable oil blend. Visit today!', 101),
  ('poutine', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Poutine', 'Snacks & Sides', 'Rich and tasty gravy? Melty, mouth-watering cheese curds? On our World Famous Fries? You better believe it!', 102),
  ('fruit-fibre-muffin', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Fruit & Fibre Muffin', 'Snacks & Sides', 'A perfect companion to coffee; a quick-and-easy mid-morning or afternoon treat. With a choice of five delectable flavours including Banana Chocolate Chunk, Blueberry, Carrot, Fruit ''n Fibre and Cranberry Orange. Enjoy one today!', 103),
  ('blueberry-muffin', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Blueberry Muffin', 'Snacks & Sides', 'A perfect companion to coffee; a quick-and-easy mid-morning or afternoon treat. With a choice of five delectable flavours including Banana Chocolate Chunk, Blueberry, Carrot, Fruit ''n Fibre and Cranberry Orange. Enjoy one today!', 104),
  ('carrot-muffin', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Carrot Muffin', 'Snacks & Sides', 'A perfect companion to coffee; a quick-and-easy mid-morning or afternoon treat. With a choice of five delectable flavours including Banana Chocolate Chunk, Blueberry, Carrot, Fruit ''n Fibre and Cranberry Orange. Enjoy one today!', 105),
  ('cranberry-orange-muffin-201057', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Cranberry Orange Muffin', 'Snacks & Sides', 'A perfect companion to coffee; a quick-and-easy mid-morning or afternoon treat. With a choice of five delectable flavours including Banana Chocolate Chunk, Blueberry, Carrot, Fruit ''n Fibre and Cranberry Orange. Enjoy one today!', 106),
  ('baked-apple-pie', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Baked Apple Pie', 'Snacks & Sides', 'It''s the tradition you love to uphold, with delicious apples lightly spiced with cinnamon in a flaky crust, baked fresh daily.', 107),
  ('cadbury-creme-egg-mcflurry-regular', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Cadbury Creme Egg McFlurry', 'Desserts & Shakes', 'Smooth vanilla soft serve blended with pieces of milk chocolate then swirled together with the delicious flavour of sweet Cadbury Creme Egg fondant all whipped together for a decadent cool and creamy dessert.', 108),
  ('triple-thick-shamrock-shake-syrup-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Shamrock Shake', 'Desserts & Shakes', 'A classic flavour is back for a limited time only! The delicious and refreshing taste of mint is back in our iconic Shamrock Shake.', 109),
  ('salted-caramel-mcFlurry-regular', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Salted Caramel McFlurry', 'Desserts & Shakes', 'Unwrap a new favourite McFlurry flavour this holiday season, with caramel sauce and a crunchy salted caramel topping, swirled into smooth vanilla soft serve.', 110),
  ('sundae-strawberry', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Strawberry Sundae', 'Desserts & Shakes', 'Smooth and creamy vanilla soft serve, topped with strawberry sauce.', 111),
  ('cone-vanilla', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Vanilla Cone', 'Desserts & Shakes', 'Make time for a moment of sweetness with creamy vanilla soft served in a crispy cone.', 112),
  ('sundae-hot-fudge', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Hot Fudge Sundae', 'Desserts & Shakes', 'Smooth and creamy vanilla soft serve, topped with decadent hot fudge sauce. Mmmm!', 113),
  ('sundae-hot-caramel', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Hot Caramel Sundae', 'Desserts & Shakes', 'Smooth and creamy vanilla soft serve, topped with your choice of yummy caramel sauce. Mmmm!', 114),
  ('mcflurry-oreo-regular-size-portion', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Oreo McFlurry', 'Desserts & Shakes', 'Deliciousness starts with creamy vanilla soft serve swirled together with crunchy Oreo cookies. Walk in to your nearest McDonald''s and enjoy the yummy taste. Order today!', 115),
  ('mcflurry-dessert-crushed-skor-candy-bars-regular-size-portion', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'SKOR McFlurry', 'Desserts & Shakes', 'Deliciousness starts with creamy vanilla soft serve swirled together with pieces of SKOR bar. Walk in to your nearest McDonald''s and enjoy the yummy taste. Order today!
<br>
<br>
<b>SKOR ALLERGY ALERT: Contains ALMONDS. View Ingredients and Allergens for full information.</b>', 116),
  ('smarties-mcflurry-regular-size-portion', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Smarties McFlurry', 'Desserts & Shakes', 'Delicious starts with creamy vanilla soft serve swirled together with crushed Smarties. No artificial colours or flavours.', 117),
  ('triple-thick-milkshake-chocolate-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Chocolate Triple Thick Milkshake', 'Desserts & Shakes', 'Thick, smooth, and deliciously creamy soft serve, mixed with your choice of decadent chocolate, strawberry, or vanilla flavoured syrup for an extra taste of yumminess.', 118),
  ('triple-thick-milkshake-vanilla-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Vanilla Triple Thick Milkshake', 'Desserts & Shakes', 'Thick, smooth, and deliciously creamy soft serve, mixed with your choice of decadent chocolate, strawberry, or vanilla flavoured syrup for an extra taste of yumminess.', 119),
  ('triple-thick-milkshake-strawberry-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Strawberry Triple Thick Milkshake', 'Desserts & Shakes', 'Thick, smooth, and deliciously creamy soft serve, mixed with your choice of decadent chocolate, strawberry, or vanilla flavoured syrup for an extra taste of yumminess.', 120),
  ('strawberry-flavoured-yogurt-tube', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Yogurt Tube', 'Desserts & Shakes', 'Strawberry Yogurt Tube', 121),
  ('strawberry-banana-smoothie-with-yogurt-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Strawberry Banana Real Fruit Smoothie', 'Beverages', 'Get a taste of real strawberry and banana puree blended to perfection with ice. Enjoy it with or without yogurt in small, medium and large', 123),
  ('blueberry-pomegranate-smoothie-with-yogurt-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Blueberry Pomegranate Real Fruit Smoothie', 'Beverages', 'Made with real fruit puree and ice, it''s a refreshing way to enjoy the taste of blueberries and pomegranate. Try yours with or without yogurt.', 124),
  ('mango-pineapple-smoothie-with-yogurt-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Mango Pineapple Real Fruit Smoothie', 'Beverages', 'Blended with ice, real mango and pineapple puree. Enjoy it with or without yogurt.', 125),
  ('watermelon-lime-fruit-splash-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Watermelon Lime Fruit Splash', 'Beverages', 'A refreshing lemonade beverage made with real lemon juice concentrate and real lemon pulp, with the sweet and tangy taste of watermelon and lime. Served over ice.', 126),
  ('lemon-fruit-splash-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Lemon Fruit Splash', 'Beverages', 'A refreshing lemonade beverage made with real lemon juice concentrate and real lemon pulp. Served over ice.', 127),
  ('fuze-iced-tea-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Fuze Iced Tea', 'Beverages', 'A refreshing blend of real tea and natural lemon flavour, served ice cold.', 128),
  ('fruitopia-strawberry-passion-awareness-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Fruitopia Strawberry Passion Awareness', 'Beverages', 'Real fruit beverage with added vitamin C, no artificial flavours and no caffeine.', 129),
  ('fruitopia-orange-groove-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Fruitopia Orange Groove', 'Beverages', 'Real fruit beverage with added vitamin C, no artificial flavours and no caffeine', 130),
  ('coca-cola-zero-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Coca-Cola Zero', 'Beverages', 'Real Coca-Cola taste with zero calories and zero sugar. Perfection on ice.', 131),
  ('coca-cola-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Coca-Cola', 'Beverages', 'Enjoy your favourite McDonald''s meal with a Coke. The original, refreshing ice-cold cola that goes well with your meal and completes the experience. Learn more!', 132),
  ('diet-coke-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Diet Coke', 'Beverages', 'Enjoy your favourite McDonald''s meal with a Diet Coke. A refreshing ice cold cola with a light taste that goes well with your meal and completes the experience. Learn more!', 133),
  ('orange-juice-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Minute Maid Orange Juice*', 'Beverages', 'Start your day with the goodness of pure orange juice*. No preservatives. No sugar added. An excellent source of vitamin C. *From concentrate.', 134),
  ('apple-juice-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Minute Maid Apple Juice*', 'Beverages', 'Enjoy the goodness of pure apple juice*.   No preservatives. No sugar added. An excellent source of vitamin C.*From concentrate. Apple juice enriched with vitamin C.', 135),
  ('1-partly-skimmed-milk-250-ml', 'mcdonalds-canada', '1% Partly Skimmed Milk - 250 ml', 'Beverages', 'Wholesome, delicious, low fat milk; a source of Vitamin A and an excellent source of calcium. Available in 1% chocolate milk too!', 136),
  ('1-partly-skimmed-chocolate-milk', 'mcdonalds-canada', '1% Partly Skimmed Chocolate Milk - 250 ml', 'Beverages', 'Wholesome, delicious, low fat chocolate milk; a source of Vitamin A and an excellent source of calcium. Available in 1% milk too!', 137),
  ('barqs-root-beer-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Barq''s Root Beer', 'Beverages', 'Get a tasty kick from every sip of ice cold Barq''s.', 138),
  ('sprite-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Sprite', 'Beverages', 'The great taste of crisp, clear, Sprite. Made with 100% natural lemon-lime flavours, with no colours and no caffeine.', 139),
  ('dasani-water', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Dasani Water', 'Beverages', 'Quench your thirst with a bottle of cool and refreshing Dasani water. Add a bottle to your meal order today!', 140),
  ('salted-caramel-latte-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Salted Caramel Latte', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Treat yourself with the smooth and creamy Salted Caramel Latte, made with our signature McCafe espresso and topped with fresh Canadian milk, steamed and frothed. Visit today!', 141),
  ('salted-caramel-iced-coffee-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Salted Caramel Iced Coffee', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Cool and refreshing, Premium Roast Coffee on ice, brewed from 100% Arabica beans, and made for you with your choice of 2% milk or cream. To suit your taste buds, choose between: regular, French Vanilla, Sugar-Free Vanilla or Salted Caramel.', 142),
  ('oat-iced-coffee-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'McCafe Premium Roast Brewed Oat Iced Coffee', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Cool and refreshing, Premium Roast Coffee on ice, brewed from 100% Arabica beans, and made for you with smooth and creamy oat beverage.', 143),
  ('berry-mcpops', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Berry McPops', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Mini pink powdered donut with a berries and cherry filling.', 144),
  ('white-chocolate-mcpops', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'White Chocolate McPops', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Mini powdered donut with white chocolate filling.', 145),
  ('hazelnut-cocoa-mcpops', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Hazelnut & Cocoa McPops', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Mini donut with hazelnut filling, dusted with cocoa powder.', 146),
  ('coffee-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Premium Roast Brewed Coffee', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Brewed from 100% Arabica beans, fire-roasted for a rich, delicious full-bodied flavour  -  in your choice of regular or decaf.', 147),
  ('premium-tea-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Premium Tea', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Relax. It''s your time to enjoy a long, slow sip of delicious and delectable tea. Choose from Orange Pekoe, Earl Grey, Peppermint or Green Tea - and enjoy.', 148),
  ('cappuccino-with-2-milk-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Cappuccino - 2% milk', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Our Cappuccino is bold and classic, made with our signature McCafe espresso topped with fresh Canadian milk, steamed and frothed.', 149),
  ('latte-with-2-milk-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Latte - 2% milk', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Treat yourself with the smooth and sophisticated Latte, made with our signature McCafe espresso and topped with fresh Canadian milk, steamed and frothed. Visit today!', 150),
  ('french-vanilla-latte-with-2-milk-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'French Vanilla Latte', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Treat yourself with the smooth and creamy French Vanilla Latte, made with our signature McCafe espresso and topped with fresh Canadian milk, steamed and frothed. Visit today!', 151),
  ('latte-with-sugar-free-syrup-with-2-milk-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Latte with Sugar Free Syrup - 2% milk', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Enjoy our Latte with Sugar Free syrup, made with our signature McCafe espresso and topped with fresh Canadian milk, steamed and frothed. Try one at McDonald''s!', 152),
  ('caramel-latte-with-2-milk-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Caramel Latte - 2% milk', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Our Latte is smooth and sophisticated, made with our signature  McCafe espresso and topped with fresh Canadian milk, steamed and frothed. When you''re in the mood for something special, add your choice of a French vanilla, sugar-free vanilla, or caramel flavour shot.', 153),
  ('mocha-with-2-milk-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Mocha', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Made with 100% ethically sourced Arabica bean espresso, fresh milk, steamed and frothed, real whipped cream and chocolate syrup with a perfect balance of sweetness, vanilla and chocolate. Made with no artificial colours or flavours.', 154),
  ('espresso', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Espresso', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Get ready for a McCafe Espresso  -  a bold boost of rich flavour from our freshly ground espresso, made from 100% Arabica beans.', 155),
  ('double-espresso', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Double Espresso', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Get ready for a McCafe Espresso  -  a bold boost of rich flavour from our freshly ground espresso, made from 100% Arabica beans.', 156),
  ('americano-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Americano', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Our Americano is bold and robust, made with our signature McCafe  espresso combined with hot water, for coffee aficionados who prefer a bolder cup.', 157),
  ('hot-chocolate-with-2-milk-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Hot Chocolate', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'A hot chocolate made with a perfect balance of sweetness, vanilla, chocolate and steamed milk. Made with no artificial colours or flavours.', 158),
  ('higgins-burke-hot-chocolate', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Higgins & Burke Hot Chocolate', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Higgins & Burke Hot Chocolate', 159),
  ('iced-coffee-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Premium Roast Brewed Iced Coffee', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Cool and refreshing, premium roast coffee on ice, brewed from 100% Arabica beans, and made for you with your choice of 2% milk or cream. To suit your taste buds, choose between: regular, vanilla, sugar-free vanilla or caramel.', 160),
  ('vanilla-iced-coffee-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'French Vanilla Iced Coffee', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Cool and refreshing, Premium Roast Coffee on ice, brewed from 100% Arabica beans, and made for you with your choice of 2% milk or cream. To suit your taste buds, choose between: regular, French Vanilla, Sugar-Free Vanilla or Salted Caramel.', 161),
  ('caramel-iced-coffee-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Caramel Iced Coffee', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Made from McCafe top roast coffee, for the same rich creamy and delicious taste. Enjoy it as you like, with cream milk, black or sweet.', 162),
  ('coffee-iced-frapp-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Coffee Frappe', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Coffee Frappe is made with the great taste of 100% Arabica beans in a creamy dairy base, freshly blended with ice for a deep, down cool and sweet creamy taste consistent from first sip to last. Made with no artificial flavours or colours.', 163),
  ('iced-coffee-with-sugar-free-syrup-medium', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Iced Coffee with Sugar Free syrup', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Cool and refreshing, Premium Roast Coffee on ice, brewed from 100% Arabica beans, and made for you with your choice of 2% milk or cream. Try it with a flavour shot; choose from vanilla, sugar free syrup or caramel.', 164),
  ('vanilla-chai-iced-frapp-small', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Vanilla Chai Frappe', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'McCafe Vanilla Chai Iced Frappe is made with the refreshingly exotic combination of vanilla and chai flavours, including cinnamon and nutmeg, in a creamy dairy base, freshly blended with ice for a balanced deep, down cool, consistent from first sip to last. Made with no artificial flavours or colours.', 165),
  ('chocolate-brownie-muffin', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Chocolate Brownie Muffin', 'McCafe & Bakery', 'Baked fresh daily and moist like a brownie, with the decadent taste of chocolate mixed with sweet chocolate chips and topped with crunchy brownie pieces.', 166),
  ('french-fries-small-mcpicks', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'World Famous Fries - Small', 'McPicks', 'McDonald''s World Famous Fries are always a delicious choice. Cut from whole potatoes grown on Canadian farms, our fries are cooked to golden perfection in a vegetable oil blend. Mmmm... of course you want fries with that!', 167),
  ('banana-chocolate-chunk-muffin', 'mcdonalds-canada', 'Banana Chocolate Chunk Muffin', 'McPicks', 'A perfect companion to coffee; a quick-and-easy mid-morning or afternoon treat.  With a choice of five delectable flavours including Banana Chocolate Chunk, Blueberry, Carrot, Fruit ''n Fibre and Cranberry Orange.  Enjoy one today!', 168),
  ('baked-apple-pie-200553', 'mcdonalds-canada', '2 Baked Apple Pies', 'McPicks', 'Twice the enjoyment, with two Baked Apple Pies! It''s the tradition you love to uphold, with delicious apples lightly spiced with cinnamon in a flaky crust, baked fresh daily.', 169)
